\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
By Lemma 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "lem:Newton_step"

\end_inset

, we have
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mx^{-1}\delta_{x}=(\mi-\mproj)(\overline{\delta}_{\mu}/\overline{\mu})
